      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Green Light Chess</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg/330px-Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg/500px-Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg/960px-Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Gachala_Emerald_3526711557_849c4c7367.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shades_of_green#Emerald\">Emerald green</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Green Light Chess</b>, (Green Light, GLChess <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>)<br />\na <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> compliant chess engine by <a href=\"/Tim_Foden\" title=\"Tim Foden\">Tim Foden</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, version 2.09 relying on an own 32-bit <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Tournament_Play\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournament Play</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Description\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Green Light started its life in early 1997 as <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a> engine, and since version 2.xx evolved to <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboards</a> with an <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 board</a>. \nIt applies <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> inside an <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">iterative deepening</a> framework with  <a href=\"/Depth#FractionalPlies\" title=\"Depth\">fractional ply</a> <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extensions</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">transposition table</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Null Move Reductions\">null move reductions</a>, <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">razoring</a>, and <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">pruning</a> in <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">quiescence search</a> based on <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE</a>. \nIn version 2.14, <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning#TDLamba\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">TD-λ</a> learning was implemented which required <a href=\"/Millipawns\" title=\"Millipawns\">milli-pawn values</a> rather than <a href=\"/Centipawns\" title=\"Centipawns\">centi-pawn values</a>. \nThe well maintained 2.18 change log gives a decent overview of features, modifications and bugfixes within the engine development, its GUI and WinBoard implementations <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournament_Play\">Tournament Play</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Tournament Play\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Green Light Chess felt well in the green-light flooded cave in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graz\">Graz</a> and played a strong <a href=\"/WCCC_2003\" title=\"WCCC 2003\">WCCC 2003</a> with a respectable fifth place and 6 points out of 11, and further played the <a href=\"/CCT6\" title=\"CCT6\">CCT6</a> with 5½ out of 9. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/WCCC_2003\" title=\"WCCC 2003\">WCCC 2003</a>, round 5, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Green Light</a> - <a href=\"/Falcon\" title=\"Falcon\">Falcon</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"WCCC 2003\"]\n[Site \"Graz, Austria\"]\n[Date \"2003.11.25\"]\n[Round \"5\"]\n[White \"Green Light\"]\n[Black \"Falcon\"]\n[Result \"1-0\"]\n\n1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 d6 3.d4 cxd4 4.Qxd4 a6 5.Qe3 Nc6 6.Nc3 Nf6 7.Bd2 Ng4 8.Qe2 g6 \n9.h3 Nge5 10.Nxe5 dxe5 11.O-O-O Nd4 12.Qc4 Be6 13.Qb4 Bd7 14.Be3 e6 15.Qc4 \nRc8 16.Qd3 Bc5 17.f4 f6 18.fxe5 fxe5 19.h4 O-O 20.h5 Be8 21.Bd2 Bb4 22.hxg6 \nBxg6 23.Qe3 Qa5 24.Kb1 Qb6 25.Rh6 Rc7 26.Qg3 Rg7 27.Qe3 Ba3 28.Na4 Qc6 \n29.Nc3 Bc5 30.Qh3 b5 31.Bd3 b4 32.Ne2 Nxe2 33.Bxe2 Rf2 34.Bd3 a5 35.Be1 Rf8 \n36.Bg3 Be3 37.Rh4 Bd4 38.Rg4 Qc5 39.Rg5 Re8 40.Rh1 Qc7 41.Qh2 Ra8 42.Bxe5 \nBxe5 43.Qxe5 Qxe5 44.Rxe5 Bf7 45.Rg1 Rg3 46.Be2 Kh8 47.Bf3 Rag8 48.Rc1 R3g5 \n49.Rxg5 Rxg5 50.c3 bxc3 51.Rxc3 Kg7 52.Kc2 Kf6 53.Kd3 Bh5 54.Bxh5 Rxh5 \n55.Kd4 Rg5 56.g3 Rb5 57.b3 Rg5 58.Re3 Rg8 59.e5+ Kf5 60.a3 Rd8+ 61.Kc5 Rd1 \n62.Kb6 Rd5 63.b4 axb4 64.axb4 Rd1 65.b5 h5 66.Kb7 h4 67.gxh4 Rh1 68.b6 Rxh4 \n69.Rb3 Kxe5 70.Kc6 Rc4+ 71.Kd7 Rh4 72.b7 Rh8 73.b8=Q+ Rxb8 1-0 \n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=141909\">Version 2.11 of Green Light Chess released; web page moved</a> by <a href=\"/Tim_Foden\" title=\"Tim Foden\">Tim Foden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=192394\">Green Light Chess v2.15 now released</a> by <a href=\"/Tim_Foden\" title=\"Tim Foden\">Tim Foden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=48455\">GLC and others when using wb2uci</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 03, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Wb2UCI\" title=\"Wb2UCI\">Wb2UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32361\">Comet B15, Amy 0.6 Green Light Chess 2.07a available ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 04, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Comet\" title=\"Comet\">Comet</a>, <a href=\"/Amy\" title=\"Amy\">Amy</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.7sun.com/chess/index.php\">Green Light Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=119\">Green Light (ICGA Tournaments)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirr.homeunix.org/chess/engines/Norbert%27s%20collection/Green%20Light%20Chess%20%28Compilation%29/\">Index of /chess/engines/Norbert's collection/Green Light Chess (Compilation)</a> compiled by <a href=\"/Norbert_Raimund_Leisner\" title=\"Norbert Raimund Leisner\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/Kirill_Kryukov\" title=\"Kirill Kryukov\">Kirill Kryukov</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Green%20Light%20Chess%203.01.2.2#Green_Light_Chess_3_01_2_2\">Green Light Chess 3.01.2.2</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/40</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/404/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Green%20Light%20Chess%203.01.2.2#Green_Light_Chess_3_01_2_2\">Green Light Chess 3.01.2.2</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/4</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/kcec/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Green%20Light%20Chess%203.00\">Green Light Chess 3.00</a> in <a href=\"/KCEC\" title=\"KCEC\">KCEC</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Light\">Green Light (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green-light\">Green-light from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fishing_light_attractor\">Fishing light attractor from Wikipedia</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Light_Trust\">Green Light Trust from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_fireballs\">Green fireballs from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_flash\">Green flash from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_%28disambiguation%29\">Green (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green\">Green (color) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shades_of_green\">Shades of green from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Light\">Light from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electromagnetic_spectrum\">Electromagnetic spectrum from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aurora_%28astronomy%29\">Aurora (astronomy) from Wikipedia</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Aurora_borealis_over_Eielson_Air_Force_Base,_Alaska.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aurora borealis over Eielson Air Force Base, Alaska.jpg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Aurora_borealis_over_Eielson_Air_Force_Base%2C_Alaska.jpg/960px-Aurora_borealis_over_Eielson_Air_Force_Base%2C_Alaska.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"417\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Aurora_borealis_over_Eielson_Air_Force_Base%2C_Alaska.jpg/1280px-Aurora_borealis_over_Eielson_Air_Force_Base%2C_Alaska.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Light_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gachal%C3%A1_Emerald\">Gachala Emerald</a> from the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Museum_of_Natural_History\">National Museum of Natural History</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Washington,_D.C.\">Washington, D.C.</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shades_of_green\">Shades of green from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">not to be confused with the <a href=\"/index.php?title=GlChess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"GlChess (page does not exist)\">glChess</a> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.7sun.com/chess/oldversions/218/index.php#win32-gui\">Green Light Chess - WIN32 GUI</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirr.homeunix.org/chess/engines/Norbert%27s%20collection/Green%20Light%20Chess%20%28Compilation%29/v2.18/changes.txt\">changes.txt</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/round.php?tournament=2&amp;round=5&amp;id=7\">Graz 2003 - Chess - Round 5 - Game 7 (ICGA Tournaments)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aurora_%28astronomy%29\">Aurora Borealis</a>, or Northern Lights, shines above <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bear_Lake_%28Alaska%29\">Bear Lake</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eielson_Air_Force_Base\">Eielson Air Force Base</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alaska\">Alaska</a>, January 18, 2005, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States_Air_Force\">United States Air Force</a> photo by Senior Airman Joshua Strang</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Epaullu/Aurora/aurora.html\">The Aurora Distributed Shared Data System</a> by <a href=\"/Paul_Lu\" title=\"Paul Lu\">Paul Lu</a></span>\n</li>\n</o